Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:34.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\ngood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:36.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When he visits\nhis fiancée,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:40.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the young man saw a young\Nwoman struggling to fight destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:48.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, none of them are yet aware of the\Ncruel fate that is silently bearing down on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.89,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,352)}Act 7:\NThe Secret Flower Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:32.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:46.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:48.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:55.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't feeling well.\NHaidee is unaccustomed to crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:03:00.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't concern yourself.\NWe will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:31.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it was\nthat Haidee saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:34.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She looked as if she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:49.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You saw him?\NYou saw that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:02.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that you are\nengaged to be married...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:19.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't think I will be able\nto restrain myself tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NPlease excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Haidee\nis okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:31.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about the\NCount's mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:36.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't like that.\NHe cares for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like a master is kind towards\nhis pet dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put the Count on the same level\nas people like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Count and Haidee have...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:50.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A relationship as two independent adults.\NWhere they both care for each other and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about other people.\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel\nabout Eugenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one\nto talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:08.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"The aristocracy doesn't marry for love,\nthey marry for money and honor."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:12.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is what Maximilien said\nstill bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was right. As much\nas I hate to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's how marriages work,\nyou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:21.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting married\nbecause I want to, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Baron Franz d'Epinay!\NI'd like a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you with\nyour fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How is that any of\nyour business?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you love her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:47.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I like her as just\nanother girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can you talk\nlike that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:57.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Maximilien!\NLet me handle this. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:01.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If she's your fiancée,\Nyou should love her with all your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to\nsay it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I said what was on my mind,\nthat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're too irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:21.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been in love with someone,\nnot like he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:26.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, what do you think it\Nmeans to be in love with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:41.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you do what you can\nto straighten this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:45.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hey!\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go through\nwith it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it like we planned,\nand you'll do fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First off,\nyou compliment her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Compliment her?\NOn what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:17.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On anything! Her dress!\NHer makeup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:26.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's Crown Prosecutor Villefort.\NHe's Valentine's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even small-time crooks get the death penalty\nwhen he gets his hands on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:43.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's Valentine's mother.\NThey're not related by blood, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edouard! Come here\nthis instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:51.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edouard, her younger brother.\NHe and Valentine have different mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look. Aren't these\nbeautiful horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hate horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, he can be such a handful.\NI'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:04.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is Valentine coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That girl seems to prefer\nstaying at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hate Valentine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:57.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mademoiselle, the Viscount Albert\nde Morcerf is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:03.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:15.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think he has something that\nhe wants to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:24.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I have to prepare\nmy grandfather's dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:28.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:33.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've fallen in love\nwith you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, our plans have\ngone out the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:48.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough from you! I'll talk to\nher first, so you go wait over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think she knows that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:57.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if we startled you.\NThis wasn't what we had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been\nmaking fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:03.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! He meant it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?\NWhy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien meant\nwhat he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:13.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a little... clumsy\nat expressing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:17.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear what he has to say. I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:24.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz has told me\nhow he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:31.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He says that he only thinks of you as the\nfiancée chosen for him by his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you feel the same way,\ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:41.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he says you should\ndo what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:46.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He might not have a title, but Maximilien\nis a fine soldier and an honest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:50.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And most important of all,\nhe's deeply in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that he'll\nmake you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No one... No one considers\nwhat I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will now pass judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:20.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The defendant is found guilty of the crimes\nof larceny and insulting the aristocracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and is hereby sentenced\nto death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There were extenuating\ncircumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get no sympathy\nfrom me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:32.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Trash like you disturb the\npublic order of the kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:56.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Do you miss\nthe outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting along\nwith Valentine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that you\nbeat her severely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:10.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth\ntold you that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:16.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I like to think that I'm attentive\nas can be to that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:20.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just because she's the daughter of\Nhis old wife doesn't mean that l...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Driver? Aren't we going\na little too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:28.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me, Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:33.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The horses!\NThey aren't obeying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:02.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are not harmed,\NI trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why, it's the Count\nof Monte Cristo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have you to thank\nfor our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:19.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was fortunate indeed that I had on hand\none who is skilled in the handling of horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:23.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You look weird!\NAre you an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such\na rascal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:30.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Curiosity is a sign\nof intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know\nyour name...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Count\nof Monte Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He and my husband\nare practically family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard something about you buying\nthe late Prince's booth at the opera...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:47.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:51.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is not my custom to attract\nundue attention to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but there were no other\nseats to be had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Héloise, the wife of\NCrown Prosecutor Villefort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then one might say that you are the\nwife of Paris' guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a flatterer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your horses still seem\nto be agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Allow us to return you\nto your homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If the good Madame Villefort is amenable,\NI shall see to it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen her\nlike that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Madame has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Barrois! Tea for our guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, that won't be\nnecessary, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:50.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, call me Héloise, Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine! We have\na visitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:02.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mademoiselle says that\nshe is feeling unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:06.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, that girl...\NValentine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:09.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even come out\Nand say hello to our guest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She is utterly miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:17.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:23.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down, her heart\nyearns for freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But she is averting her eyes\nfrom those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She is delicate\nand fragile!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear her soul\ncrying out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it,\nall right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It says, "No one considers\nwhat I want."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:43.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't. Neither do you.\NNone of us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:49.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is always making\ntrouble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:54.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she gets it from her late mother.\NShe's sickly and stays cooped up indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:59.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying my best to raise her\nto be more sociable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"She's gonna die young."\NIsn't that what you said, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:08.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edouard! You and\nyour nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for my\nown child, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine stands to inherit the fortune\nof her grandfather, Monsieur Noirtier,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as well has that of the Marquis Saint-Meran\Non her mother's side,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but this boy will\nreceive nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It saddens me\nto hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:31.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Siblings should be equally fortunate,\Neven if unrelated by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's got fangs\nlike a vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edouard!\NYou're making me angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire! Vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's a blue-faced vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, he's such\na rude boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:50.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, he is\na darling child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:55.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To apologize for his behavior, shall\NI show you to my secret place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:01.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a modest little refuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:10.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there is nothing that\NI can do for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:17.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:26.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, this greenhouse is your refuge...\NIt is magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:32.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These flowers might be\nmy only friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:36.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belladonna. Mandragora. Datura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:42.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your favorite flowers all share\Na fascinating trait, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:49.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In each of them, their beautiful petals\nconceal a deadly poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:18:00.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My love of horticulture grew\ninto an interest in botany.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a woman's place to be\ninterested in such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:08.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you also have\nan interest in toxicology?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be interested\nin such horrible things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Horrible? Why should\nit be horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Toxicology and pharmacology\nare two sides of the same coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:23.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Also, nothing is more enticing\nto human beings than poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:29.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Poisons that steal a man's\nlife away in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Poisons that kill slowly\nand leave no trace of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One must wonder how\nmany poisonings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:41.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...have been consigned to the darkness,\nknown to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:48.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is a beauty to those who have\nbeen captivated by poison's charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:54.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Gentlemen don't peep into\nother people's windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:19:01.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This trinket is commonly referred to\nas a Borgia Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:05.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come. Press on the stone\nand see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:13.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that Lucrezia Borgia used\Nthese to dispatch countless people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:17.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And among her victims\nwas her own husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:21.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That ring belongs\nto you, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:28.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is nothing, a mere\ngetting-acquainted gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:56.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go somewhere\nfar away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:01.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To some faraway place where\nno one knows who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:27.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benedetto! Take a look\nout the left window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's Viscount Albert\nde Morcerf.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:12.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A party at\nthe Count's villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:16.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the labyrinth, we cross paths\nwith a beautiful, horrible past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:20.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, Act 8:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:20.92,count fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350, 352)}Act 8:\NA Night in Boulogne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:21.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."A Night in Boulogne."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:23.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
